American Fango - A coming-to-New York love story about an Italian actor who comes to New York City from Rome, and through a series of misadventures becomes romantically involved with several beautiful women. Sidetracked in Los Angeles, he is ultimately transformed by the power of true love ... and the realization that he is really a New Yorker at heart!  

2017
Stars: Joseph D'Onofrio, Deborah Twiss, Samantha Scaffidi
